<h2 id="becados">Becados</h2>

<p>The school students we are helping this year are truly doing well balancing their home life, as well as school. They are committed to their responsibilities here at the project, and faithfully come to serve weekly. Their first report cards will be released in June, and we are eager to see their progress!</p>

<p>We are forever grateful for you all, and your continued support with allows all this to happen. Knowing we have a support system around us, covering us in prayer, makes each day seem doable. Thank you from the bottom of our hearts!</p>

